1133
00:39:22.823 --> 00:39:24.743
An Andamanese came out with a bow and arrow

1134
00:39:24.743 --> 00:39:26.583
and fired at the chopper saying go away,

1135
00:39:26.583 --> 00:39:28.444
we didn't need you then we don't need you now.

1136
00:39:28.444 --> 00:39:30.663
And they realized, the Andamanese had escaped

1137
00:39:30.663 --> 00:39:33.063
the tsunami because they knew it was coming.

1138
00:39:33.063 --> 00:39:34.163
They got out of the villages,

1139
00:39:34.163 --> 00:39:35.424
they went up to the high country

1140
00:39:35.424 --> 00:39:36.663
