1141
00:39:36.663 --> 00:39:38.644
This is very relevant to all of us,

1142
00:39:38.644 --> 00:39:39.804
Shamanic dreaming people,

1143
00:39:39.804 --> 00:39:40.984
they have a lesson for all of us.

1144
00:39:40.984 --> 00:39:43.284
Number one, they live close to nature.

1145
00:39:43.284 --> 00:39:45.063
They follow the patterns of wind and wave,

1146
00:39:45.063 --> 00:39:46.924
they follow the behavior of birds and animals

1147
00:39:46.924 --> 00:39:48.344
and they know things that way.

1148
00:39:48.344 --> 00:39:50.323
Secondly, they have a process of communal,

1149
00:39:50.323 --> 00:39:51.404
collective dreaming.

1150
00:39:51.404 --> 00:39:53.663
They get together in their big houses

1151
00:39:53.663 --> 00:39:55.684
to dream on, often survival matters.

1152
00:39:55.684 --> 00:39:57.124
Where do we find the fish?

1153
00:39:57.124 --> 00:39:58.763
Where do we find the food?

1154
00:39:58.763 --> 00:40:00.183
What is going to happen next?

1155
00:40:00.183 --> 00:40:02.563
They picture themselves growing a kind of web

1156
00:40:02.563 --> 00:40:04.584
of dreaming and they state their intentions

1157
00:40:04.584 --> 00:40:06.663
